name: basak006/User-Interface-Design_Final-Project
description: Developed a Drawing Application in Java using Netbeans as the Integrated Development Environment. The user could draw various geometric shapes and use a color palette to decide color of the objects. One could clear the graphics on the drawing area and drag the last drawn object to a different position using the hand button. File options were provided. The mouse tracking capability showed the present position of the mouse. The drawing area could also be zoomed in and zoomed out by a factor of 25.
